\subsection{Satake Angles}
\begin{definition}\label{cmf.satake_angles}
\uses{cmf.satake_parameters}
The **Satake angles** $\theta_p = \arg \alpha_p \in [-\pi, \pi]$ are the arguments of a complex embedding of the {{KNOWL('cmf.satake_parameters', 'Satake parameters')}} $\alpha_p$.
\end{definition}


